A British woman sentenced to three months in a Dubai jail after being found guilty of having drunken sex in the back of a taxi has said it is not fair she has had 'to rot' in the country 'for something I didn't do'.

Rebecca Blake, who turns 30 today, finds out tomorrow whether she will go to jail or be deported after appealing her initial sentence.

She is currently on bail along with Irishman Conor McRedmond, with whom she was caught.

